metadata.title: Gilani welcomes students, faculty of Greenland Public School to Senate

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Jun 16 (APP): Chairman Senate Syed Yusuf Raza Gilani on Monday welcomed the students and faculty members of Greenland Public School System, Rawat, Bhurban, and Murree during the proceedings of the Upper House. The students visited the Parliament House and witnessed the Senate proceedings from the visitorsa gallery. Chairman Gilani formally acknowledged their presence and extended his warm greetings.
